== 隐藏字体 ==
Apple Garamond 仅随 Mac OS X 10.2 发布，并隐藏在<br/>
<tt style="white-space:nowrap"><small>/System/Library/CoreServices/Setup Assistant.app/Contents/Resources/Setup Assistant.dfont</small></tt>

Apple Casual隐藏在：<br/>
<tt style="white-space:nowrap"><small>/System/Library/Components/Ink.component/Contents/SharedSupport/InkServer.app/Contents/Resources/AppleCasual.dfont</small></tt>

iDVD附带很多字体但是却不会自动安装，这些字体位于：<br/>
<tt style="white-space:nowrap"><small>/Applications/iDVD.app/Contents/Resources/Fonts/</small></tt>

Matrix Ticker位于：<br/>
<tt style="white-space:nowrap"><small>/Library/Widgets/ESPN.wdgt/ESPNTicker.dfont</small></tt>

